---
import { COMPANY_NAME } from "../../data/consts";
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-sky-50 overflow-hidden observe-section">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <span
        class="text-sky-600 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 block"
        >Financial Transparency</span
      >
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 leading-tight">
        Honest Talk About<br />
        <span class="text-sky-600 italic">Cost & Time</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-xl shadow-slate-200/60 border border-slate-100 overflow-hidden mb-12"
      >
        <div class="p-8 md:p-12 border-b border-slate-50">
          <h3
            class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-6 h-6 text-sky-500"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            Professional Pathways (Career Flying)
          </h3>

          <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none mb-10">
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Zero-to-airline programs typically require 12–18 months at
              large-scale national academies. By treating training like a
              full-time professional commitment, our students consistently
              complete the track in <strong class="text-slate-900"
                >8–10 months</strong
              > without cutting corners on safety or proficiency.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div
              class="bg-sky-600 rounded-3xl p-8 text-white relative overflow-hidden group"
            >
              <div
                class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-2xl group-hover:scale-150 transition-transform duration-700"
              >
              </div>
              <p
                class="text-sky-100 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2"
              >
                Our All-In Cost
              </p>
              <h4 class="text-4xl font-black mb-2">$89,500</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-sky-100 leading-relaxed">
                Through CFII. All ratings, instruction, and aircraft time
                included.
              </p>

              <div
                class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold bg-white/10 w-fit px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-white/20"
              >
                <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"
                ></span>
                Part 141 Standard
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-sky-50 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-slate-200">
              <p
                class="text-slate-400 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2"
              >
                National Average
              </p>
              <h4 class="text-4xl font-black text-slate-300 mb-2">
                $120K - $140K
              </h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
                Typical range at large national academies for the same
                certifications.
              </p>

              <div
                class="mt-6 text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider"
              >
                * Based on 2024-2025 Industry Data
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-sky-900 p-8 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
          <p
            class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto relative z-10"
          >
            <strong class="text-white">Why the difference?</strong> We don't spend
            millions on national advertising. Our investment goes directly into <span
              class="text-sky-400">superior aircraft maintenance</span
            > and <span class="text-sky-400">senior instructor pay</span>,
            passing the marketing savings directly to our students.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6">
        <a
          href="/enroll"
          class="w-full md:w-auto px-10 py-5 bg-sky-600 text-white font-black rounded-2xl hover:bg-sky-700 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl shadow-sky-600/20 text-center"
        >
          Begin Your Enrollment
        </a>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="w-full md:w-auto px-10 py-5 bg-white text-slate-900 border border-slate-200 font-bold rounded-2xl hover:bg-sky-50 transition-all text-center"
        >
          Request Detailed Quote
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
